title: Bracelet, one of a pair
description: one of a pair of bracelets made form a piece of silver flat on one side and rounded with a dingle ridge in the center on the other side; silver piece is bent into a circle leaving a small opening a the end; etching of two frogs a center surrounded by branches(?) and semicircles; eye shaped medallion in center
creditline: The Suzanne S. Roberts Fund for Asian Art
